                                          comment: "<p>Typical side effects of <a href=\"http://www.onexamination.com/goto.aspx?url=http://www.rxlist.com/cisplatin-drug.htm#ad\" target=\"_blank\">cisplatin</a> include</p>  <ul> <li>Marrow toxicity</li>  <li>Ototoxicity</li>  <li>Peripheral neuropathy</li>  <li>Nephrotoxicity</li>  <li>Alopecia</li>  <li>Changes in taste.</li> </ul>  <p>Although optic neuritis is described it is not a typical side effect.</p>",
